timelineItems.desc: A pair of clubs in real need of points for different reasons meet when the Colorado Rapids, chasing a playoff spot, play host to Supporters’ Shield contenders Seattle Sounders FC on Sunday afternoon at Dick’s Sporting Goods Park.
